title: Zelenskyy says peace talks with Russia are close to collapse; Russia says it's not at war with NATO
content:
1. Zelenskyy says peace talks with Russia are close to collapse; Russia says it's not at war with NATO  CNBC
  2. Rockets hit Ukrainian capital Kyiv as UN chief visits the city – BBC News  BBC News
  3. UN works to broker civilian evacuation from Mariupol  The Associated Press
  4. Russia sharpens warnings as the U.S. and Europe send more weapons to Ukraine  NPR
  5. Russia does not consider itself at war with NATO, blames Kyiv for talks deadlock - agencies  Reuters
